713751f-a.title: Manhattan: 56th Street - Sutton Place South
713751f-a.text:
Detail of building of Peter Doelger's Brewery, showing statue,
probably of Gambrinus, 5dth Street, south side, between Sutton
Place and First Avenue.
October 20, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.
